lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_divne0bt: 
   shows "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( A ≠ 𝟬 ⟷ ( A \<cdiv> B ) ≠ 𝟬 )"
proof -
   have S1: "B ∈ ℂ ⟶ ( B ⋅ 𝟬 ) = 𝟬" by (rule MMI_mul01t)
   from S1 have S2: "B ∈ ℂ ⟶ ( ( B ⋅ 𝟬 ) = A ⟷ 𝟬 = A )" by (rule MMI_eqeq1d)
   have S3: "A = 𝟬 ⟷ 𝟬 = A" by (rule MMI_eqcom)
   from S2 S3 have S4: "B ∈ ℂ ⟶ ( A = 𝟬 ⟷ ( B ⋅ 𝟬 ) = A )" by (rule MMI_syl6rbbrA)
   from S4 have S5: "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( A = 𝟬 ⟷ ( B ⋅ 𝟬 ) = A )" by (rule MMI_3ad2ant2)
   have S6: "𝟬 ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_0cn)
   have S7: "( ( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ 𝟬 ∈ ℂ ) ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( A \<cdiv> B ) = 𝟬 ⟷ ( B ⋅ 𝟬 ) = A )" by (rule MMI_divmult)
   from S6 S7 have S8: "( ( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ) ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( A \<cdiv> B ) = 𝟬 ⟷ ( B ⋅ 𝟬 ) = A )" by (rule MMI_mp3anl3)
   from S8 have S9: "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( A \<cdiv> B ) = 𝟬 ⟷ ( B ⋅ 𝟬 ) = A )" by (rule MMI_3impa)
   from S5 S9 have S10: "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( A = 𝟬 ⟷ ( A \<cdiv> B ) = 𝟬 )" by (rule MMI_bitr4d)
   from S10 show "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( A ≠ 𝟬 ⟷ ( A \<cdiv> B ) ≠ 𝟬 )" by (rule MMI_eqneqd)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_divne0: assumes A1: "A ∈ ℂ" and
    A2: "B ∈ ℂ" and
    A3: "A ≠ 𝟬" and
    A4: "B ≠ 𝟬"   
   shows "( A \<cdiv> B ) ≠ 𝟬"
proof -
   from A1 have S1: "A ∈ ℂ".
   from A2 have S2: "B ∈ ℂ".
   from A4 have S3: "B ≠ 𝟬".
   from A3 have S4: "A ≠ 𝟬".
   have S5: "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( A ≠ 𝟬 ⟷ ( A \<cdiv> B ) ≠ 𝟬 )" by (rule MMI_divne0bt)
   from S4 S5 have S6: "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( A \<cdiv> B ) ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_mpbii)
   from S1 S2 S3 S6 show "( A \<cdiv> B ) ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_mp3an)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_recne0z: assumes A1: "A ∈ ℂ"   
   shows "A ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> A ) ≠ 𝟬"
proof -
   have S1: "A = 
 if ( A ≠ 𝟬 , A , 𝟭 ) ⟶ 
 ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> A ) = 
 ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> if ( A ≠ 𝟬 , A , 𝟭 ) )" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   from S1 have S2: "A = 
 if ( A ≠ 𝟬 , A , 𝟭 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> A ) ≠ 𝟬 ⟷ 
 ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> if ( A ≠ 𝟬 , A , 𝟭 ) ) ≠ 𝟬 )" by (rule MMI_neeq1d)
   have S3: "𝟭 ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_1cn)
   from A1 have S4: "A ∈ ℂ".
   have S5: "𝟭 ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_1cn)
   from S4 S5 have S6: "if ( A ≠ 𝟬 , A , 𝟭 ) ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_keepel)
   have S7: "𝟭 ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_ax1ne0)
   have S8: "if ( A ≠ 𝟬 , A , 𝟭 ) ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_elimne0)
   from S3 S6 S7 S8 have S9: "( 𝟭 \<cdiv> if ( A ≠ 𝟬 , A , 𝟭 ) ) ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_divne0)
   from S2 S9 show "A ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> A ) ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_dedth)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_recne0t: 
   shows "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ A ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> A ) ≠ 𝟬"
proof -
   have S1: "A = 
 if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( A ≠ 𝟬 ⟷ if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ≠ 𝟬 )" by (rule MMI_neeq1)
   have S2: "A = 
 if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> A ) = 
 ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) )" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   from S2 have S3: "A = 
 if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> A ) ≠ 𝟬 ⟷ 
 ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ) ≠ 𝟬 )" by (rule MMI_neeq1d)
   from S1 S3 have S4: "A = 
 if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( A ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> A ) ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟷ 
 ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
 ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ) ≠ 𝟬 ) )" by (rule MMI_imbi12d)
   have S5: "𝟬 ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_0cn)
   from S5 have S6: "if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   from S6 have S7: "if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
 ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ) ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_recne0z)
   from S4 S7 have S8: "A ∈ ℂ ⟶ ( A ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> A ) ≠ 𝟬 )" by (rule MMI_dedth)
   from S8 show "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ A ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> A ) ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_imp)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_recid: assumes A1: "A ∈ ℂ" and
    A2: "A ≠ 𝟬"   
   shows "( A ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> A ) ) = 𝟭"
proof -
   from A1 have S1: "A ∈ ℂ".
   have S2: "𝟭 ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_1cn)
   from A2 have S3: "A ≠ 𝟬".
   from S1 S2 S3 show "( A ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> A ) ) = 𝟭" by (rule MMI_divcan2)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_recidz: assumes A1: "A ∈ ℂ"   
   shows "A ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ ( A ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> A ) ) = 𝟭"
proof -
   from A1 have S1: "A ∈ ℂ".
   have S2: "𝟭 ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_1cn)
   from S1 S2 show "A ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ ( A ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> A ) ) = 𝟭" by (rule MMI_divcan2z)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_recidt: 
   shows "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ A ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( A ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> A ) ) = 𝟭"
proof -
   have S1: "A = 
 if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( A ≠ 𝟬 ⟷ if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ≠ 𝟬 )" by (rule MMI_neeq1)
   have S2: "A = 
 if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 A = if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 )" by (rule MMI_id)
   have S3: "A = 
 if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> A ) = 
 ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) )" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   from S2 S3 have S4: "A = 
 if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( A ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> A ) ) = 
 ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ) )" by (rule MMI_opreq12d)
   from S4 have S5: "A = 
 if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( A ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> A ) ) = 
 𝟭 ⟷ 
 ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ) ) = 
 𝟭 )" by (rule MMI_eqeq1d)
   from S1 S5 have S6: "A = 
 if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( A ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ ( A ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> A ) ) = 𝟭 ) ⟷ 
 ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
 ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ) ) = 
 𝟭 ) )" by (rule MMI_imbi12d)
   have S7: "𝟬 ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_0cn)
   from S7 have S8: "if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   from S8 have S9: "if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
 ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ) ) = 
 𝟭" by (rule MMI_recidz)
   from S6 S9 have S10: "A ∈ ℂ ⟶ 
 ( A ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ ( A ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> A ) ) = 𝟭 )" by (rule MMI_dedth)
   from S10 show "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ A ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( A ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> A ) ) = 𝟭" by (rule MMI_imp)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_recid2t: 
   shows "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ A ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> A ) ⋅ A ) = 𝟭"
proof -
   have S1: "( ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> A ) ∈ ℂ ∧ A ∈ ℂ ) ⟶ 
 ( ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> A ) ⋅ A ) = ( A ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> A ) )" by (rule MMI_axmulcom)
   have S2: "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ A ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> A ) ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recclt)
   have S3: "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ A ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_pm3_26)
   from S1 S2 S3 have S4: "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ A ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> A ) ⋅ A ) = ( A ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> A ) )" by (rule MMI_sylanc)
   have S5: "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ A ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( A ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> A ) ) = 𝟭" by (rule MMI_recidt)
   from S4 S5 show "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ A ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> A ) ⋅ A ) = 𝟭" by (rule MMI_eqtrd)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_divrec: assumes A1: "A ∈ ℂ" and
    A2: "B ∈ ℂ" and
    A3: "B ≠ 𝟬"   
   shows "( A \<cdiv> B ) = ( A ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> B ) )"
proof -
   from A2 have S1: "B ∈ ℂ".
   from A1 have S2: "A ∈ ℂ".
   from A2 have S3: "B ∈ ℂ".
   from A3 have S4: "B ≠ 𝟬".
   from S3 S4 have S5: "( 𝟭 \<cdiv> B ) ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_reccl)
   from S2 S5 have S6: "( A ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> B ) ) ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_mulcl)
   from S1 S6 have S7: "( B ⋅ ( A ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> B ) ) ) = 
 ( ( A ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> B ) ) ⋅ B )" by (rule MMI_mulcom)
   from A1 have S8: "A ∈ ℂ".
   from S5 have S9: "( 𝟭 \<cdiv> B ) ∈ ℂ" .
   from A2 have S10: "B ∈ ℂ".
   from S8 S9 S10 have S11: "( ( A ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> B ) ) ⋅ B ) = 
 ( A ⋅ ( ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> B ) ⋅ B ) )" by (rule MMI_mulass)
   from A2 have S12: "B ∈ ℂ".
   have S13: "𝟭 ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_1cn)
   from A3 have S14: "B ≠ 𝟬".
   from S12 S13 S14 have S15: "( ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> B ) ⋅ B ) = 𝟭" by (rule MMI_divcan1)
   from S15 have S16: "( A ⋅ ( ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> B ) ⋅ B ) ) = ( A ⋅ 𝟭 )" by (rule MMI_opreq2i)
   from A1 have S17: "A ∈ ℂ".
   from S17 have S18: "( A ⋅ 𝟭 ) = A" by (rule MMI_mulid1)
   from S16 S18 have S19: "( A ⋅ ( ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> B ) ⋅ B ) ) = A" by (rule MMI_eqtr)
   from S7 S11 S19 have S20: "( B ⋅ ( A ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> B ) ) ) = A" by (rule MMI_3eqtr)
   from A1 have S21: "A ∈ ℂ".
   from A2 have S22: "B ∈ ℂ".
   from S6 have S23: "( A ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> B ) ) ∈ ℂ" .
   from A3 have S24: "B ≠ 𝟬".
   from S21 S22 S23 S24 have S25: "( A \<cdiv> B ) = 
 ( A ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> B ) ) ⟷ 
 ( B ⋅ ( A ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> B ) ) ) = A" by (rule MMI_divmul)
   from S20 S25 show "( A \<cdiv> B ) = ( A ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> B ) )" by (rule MMI_mpbir)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_divrecz: assumes A1: "A ∈ ℂ" and
    A2: "B ∈ ℂ"   
   shows "B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ ( A \<cdiv> B ) = ( A ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> B ) )"
proof -
   have S1: "B = 
 if ( B ≠ 𝟬 , B , 𝟭 ) ⟶ 
 ( A \<cdiv> B ) = 
 ( A \<cdiv> if ( B ≠ 𝟬 , B , 𝟭 ) )" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   have S2: "B = 
 if ( B ≠ 𝟬 , B , 𝟭 ) ⟶ 
 ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> B ) = 
 ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> if ( B ≠ 𝟬 , B , 𝟭 ) )" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   from S2 have S3: "B = 
 if ( B ≠ 𝟬 , B , 𝟭 ) ⟶ 
 ( A ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> B ) ) = 
 ( A ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> if ( B ≠ 𝟬 , B , 𝟭 ) ) )" by (rule MMI_opreq2d)
   from S1 S3 have S4: "B = 
 if ( B ≠ 𝟬 , B , 𝟭 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( A \<cdiv> B ) = 
 ( A ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> B ) ) ⟷ 
 ( A \<cdiv> if ( B ≠ 𝟬 , B , 𝟭 ) ) = 
 ( A ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> if ( B ≠ 𝟬 , B , 𝟭 ) ) ) )" by (rule MMI_eqeq12d)
   from A1 have S5: "A ∈ ℂ".
   from A2 have S6: "B ∈ ℂ".
   have S7: "𝟭 ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_1cn)
   from S6 S7 have S8: "if ( B ≠ 𝟬 , B , 𝟭 ) ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_keepel)
   have S9: "if ( B ≠ 𝟬 , B , 𝟭 ) ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_elimne0)
   from S5 S8 S9 have S10: "( A \<cdiv> if ( B ≠ 𝟬 , B , 𝟭 ) ) = 
 ( A ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> if ( B ≠ 𝟬 , B , 𝟭 ) ) )" by (rule MMI_divrec)
   from S4 S10 show "B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ ( A \<cdiv> B ) = ( A ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> B ) )" 
     by (rule MMI_dedth)
qed

(**********181-190*************************************)

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_divrect: 
   shows "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( A \<cdiv> B ) = ( A ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> B ) )"
proof -
   have S1: "A = 
 if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( A \<cdiv> B ) = 
 ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) \<cdiv> B )" by (rule MMI_opreq1)
   have S2: "A = 
 if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( A ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> B ) ) = 
 ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> B ) )" by (rule MMI_opreq1)
   from S1 S2 have S3: "A = 
 if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( A \<cdiv> B ) = 
 ( A ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> B ) ) ⟷ 
 ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) \<cdiv> B ) = 
 ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> B ) ) )" by (rule MMI_eqeq12d)
   from S3 have S4: "A = 
 if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ ( A \<cdiv> B ) = ( A ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> B ) ) ) ⟷ 
 ( B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
 ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) \<cdiv> B ) = 
 ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> B ) ) ) )" by (rule MMI_imbi2d)
   have S5: "B = 
 if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( B ≠ 𝟬 ⟷ if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) ≠ 𝟬 )" by (rule MMI_neeq1)
   have S6: "B = 
 if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) \<cdiv> B ) = 
 ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) \<cdiv> if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) )" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   have S7: "B = 
 if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> B ) = 
 ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) )" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   from S7 have S8: "B = 
 if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> B ) ) = 
 ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) ) )" by (rule MMI_opreq2d)
   from S6 S8 have S9: "B = 
 if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) \<cdiv> B ) = 
 ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> B ) ) ⟷ 
 ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) \<cdiv> if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) ) = 
 ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) ) ) )" by (rule MMI_eqeq12d)
   from S5 S9 have S10: "B = 
 if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) \<cdiv> B ) = ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> B ) ) ) ⟷ 
 ( if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
 ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) \<cdiv> if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) ) = 
 ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) ) ) ) )" by (rule MMI_imbi12d)
   have S11: "𝟬 ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_0cn)
   from S11 have S12: "if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   have S13: "𝟬 ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_0cn)
   from S13 have S14: "if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   from S12 S14 have S15: "if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
 ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) \<cdiv> if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) ) = 
 ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) ) )" by (rule MMI_divrecz)
   from S4 S10 S15 have S16: "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ) ⟶ 
 ( B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
 ( A \<cdiv> B ) = ( A ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> B ) ) )" by (rule MMI_dedth2h)
   from S16 show "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( A \<cdiv> B ) = ( A ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> B ) )" by (rule MMI_3impia)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_divrec2t: 
   shows "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( A \<cdiv> B ) = ( ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> B ) ⋅ A )"
proof -
   have S1: "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( A \<cdiv> B ) = ( A ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> B ) )" by (rule MMI_divrect)
   have S2: "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> B ) ∈ ℂ ) ⟶ 
 ( A ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> B ) ) = ( ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> B ) ⋅ A )" by (rule MMI_axmulcom)
   have S3: "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_3simp1)
   have S4: "( B ∈ ℂ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> B ) ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recclt)
   from S4 have S5: "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> B ) ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_3adant1)
   from S2 S3 S5 have S6: "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( A ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> B ) ) = ( ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> B ) ⋅ A )" by (rule MMI_sylanc)
   from S1 S6 show "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( A \<cdiv> B ) = ( ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> B ) ⋅ A )" by (rule MMI_eqtrd)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_divasst: 
   shows "( ( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( A ⋅ B ) \<cdiv> C ) = ( A ⋅ ( B \<cdiv> C ) )"
proof -
   have S1: "A ∈ ℂ ⟶ A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_id)
   have S2: "B ∈ ℂ ⟶ B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_id)
   have S3: "( C ∈ ℂ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> C ) ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recclt)
   from S1 S2 S3 have S4: "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ ( C ∈ ℂ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) ) ⟶ 
 ( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> C ) ∈ ℂ )" by (rule MMI_3anim123i)
   from S4 have S5: "A ∈ ℂ ⟶ 
 ( B ∈ ℂ ⟶ 
 ( ( C ∈ ℂ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> C ) ∈ ℂ ) ) )" by (rule MMI_3exp)
   from S5 have S6: "A ∈ ℂ ⟶ 
 ( B ∈ ℂ ⟶ 
 ( C ∈ ℂ ⟶ 
 ( C ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
 ( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> C ) ∈ ℂ ) ) ) )" by (rule MMI_exp4a)
   from S6 have S7: "( ( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> C ) ∈ ℂ )" by (rule MMI_3imp1)
   have S8: "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> C ) ∈ ℂ ) ⟶ 
 ( ( A ⋅ B ) ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> C ) ) = 
 ( A ⋅ ( B ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> C ) ) )" by (rule MMI_axmulass)
   from S7 S8 have S9: "( ( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( A ⋅ B ) ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> C ) ) = 
 ( A ⋅ ( B ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> C ) ) )" by (rule MMI_syl)
   have S10: "( ( A ⋅ B ) ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( A ⋅ B ) \<cdiv> C ) = 
 ( ( A ⋅ B ) ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> C ) )" by (rule MMI_divrect)
   from S10 have S11: "( ( ( A ⋅ B ) ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( A ⋅ B ) \<cdiv> C ) = 
 ( ( A ⋅ B ) ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> C ) )" by (rule MMI_3expa)
   have S12: "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ) ⟶ ( A ⋅ B ) ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_axmulcl)
   from S12 have S13: "( ( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ) ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ⟶ 
 ( ( A ⋅ B ) ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ )" by (rule MMI_anim1i)
   from S13 have S14: "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ⟶ 
 ( ( A ⋅ B ) ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ )" by (rule MMI_3impa)
   from S11 S14 have S15: "( ( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( A ⋅ B ) \<cdiv> C ) = 
 ( ( A ⋅ B ) ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> C ) )" by (rule MMI_sylan)
   have S16: "( B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( B \<cdiv> C ) = ( B ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> C ) )" by (rule MMI_divrect)
   from S16 have S17: "( ( B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( B \<cdiv> C ) = ( B ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> C ) )" by (rule MMI_3expa)
   from S17 have S18: "( ( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( B \<cdiv> C ) = ( B ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> C ) )" by (rule MMI_3adantl1)
   from S18 have S19: "( ( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( A ⋅ ( B \<cdiv> C ) ) = 
 ( A ⋅ ( B ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> C ) ) )" by (rule MMI_opreq2d)
   from S9 S15 S19 show "( ( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( A ⋅ B ) \<cdiv> C ) = ( A ⋅ ( B \<cdiv> C ) )" by (rule MMI_3eqtr4d)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_div23t: 
   shows "( ( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( A ⋅ B ) \<cdiv> C ) = ( ( A \<cdiv> C ) ⋅ B )"
proof -
   have S1: "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ) ⟶ 
 ( A ⋅ B ) = ( B ⋅ A )" by (rule MMI_axmulcom)
   from S1 have S2: "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ⟶ 
 ( A ⋅ B ) = ( B ⋅ A )" by (rule MMI_3adant3)
   from S2 have S3: "( ( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( A ⋅ B ) = ( B ⋅ A )" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   from S3 have S4: "( ( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( A ⋅ B ) \<cdiv> C ) = ( ( B ⋅ A ) \<cdiv> C )" by (rule MMI_opreq1d)
   have S5: "( ( B ∈ ℂ ∧ A ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( B ⋅ A ) \<cdiv> C ) = ( B ⋅ ( A \<cdiv> C ) )" by (rule MMI_divasst)
   from S5 have S6: "( B ∈ ℂ ∧ A ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ⟶ 
 ( C ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
 ( ( B ⋅ A ) \<cdiv> C ) = 
 ( B ⋅ ( A \<cdiv> C ) ) )" by (rule MMI_ex)
   from S6 have S7: "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ⟶ 
 ( C ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
 ( ( B ⋅ A ) \<cdiv> C ) = 
 ( B ⋅ ( A \<cdiv> C ) ) )" by (rule MMI_3com12)
   from S7 have S8: "( ( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( B ⋅ A ) \<cdiv> C ) = ( B ⋅ ( A \<cdiv> C ) )" by (rule MMI_imp)
   have S9: "( B ∈ ℂ ∧ ( A \<cdiv> C ) ∈ ℂ ) ⟶ 
 ( B ⋅ ( A \<cdiv> C ) ) = ( ( A \<cdiv> C ) ⋅ B )" by (rule MMI_axmulcom)
   have S10: "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ⟶ B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_3simp2)
   from S10 have S11: "( ( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   have S12: "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( A \<cdiv> C ) ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_divclt)
   from S12 have S13: "( ( A ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( A \<cdiv> C ) ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_3expa)
   from S13 have S14: "( ( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( A \<cdiv> C ) ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_3adantl2)
   from S9 S11 S14 have S15: "( ( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( B ⋅ ( A \<cdiv> C ) ) = ( ( A \<cdiv> C ) ⋅ B )" by (rule MMI_sylanc)
   from S4 S8 S15 show "( ( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( A ⋅ B ) \<cdiv> C ) = ( ( A \<cdiv> C ) ⋅ B )" by (rule MMI_3eqtrd)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_div13t: 
   shows "( ( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( A \<cdiv> B ) ⋅ C ) = ( ( C \<cdiv> B ) ⋅ A )"
proof -
   have S1: "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ⟶ 
 ( A ⋅ C ) = ( C ⋅ A )" by (rule MMI_axmulcom)
   from S1 have S2: "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ⟶ 
 ( ( A ⋅ C ) \<cdiv> B ) = ( ( C ⋅ A ) \<cdiv> B )" by (rule MMI_opreq1d)
   from S2 have S3: "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ⟶ 
 ( ( A ⋅ C ) \<cdiv> B ) = ( ( C ⋅ A ) \<cdiv> B )" by (rule MMI_3adant2)
   from S3 have S4: "( ( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( A ⋅ C ) \<cdiv> B ) = ( ( C ⋅ A ) \<cdiv> B )" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   have S5: "( ( A ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ) ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( A ⋅ C ) \<cdiv> B ) = ( ( A \<cdiv> B ) ⋅ C )" by (rule MMI_div23t)
   from S5 have S6: "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ) ⟶ 
 ( B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
 ( ( A ⋅ C ) \<cdiv> B ) = 
 ( ( A \<cdiv> B ) ⋅ C ) )" by (rule MMI_ex)
   from S6 have S7: "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ⟶ 
 ( B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
 ( ( A ⋅ C ) \<cdiv> B ) = 
 ( ( A \<cdiv> B ) ⋅ C ) )" by (rule MMI_3com23)
   from S7 have S8: "( ( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( A ⋅ C ) \<cdiv> B ) = ( ( A \<cdiv> B ) ⋅ C )" by (rule MMI_imp)
   have S9: "( ( C ∈ ℂ ∧ A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ) ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( C ⋅ A ) \<cdiv> B ) = ( ( C \<cdiv> B ) ⋅ A )" by (rule MMI_div23t)
   from S9 have S10: "( C ∈ ℂ ∧ A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ) ⟶ 
 ( B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
 ( ( C ⋅ A ) \<cdiv> B ) = 
 ( ( C \<cdiv> B ) ⋅ A ) )" by (rule MMI_ex)
   from S10 have S11: "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ⟶ 
 ( B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
 ( ( C ⋅ A ) \<cdiv> B ) = 
 ( ( C \<cdiv> B ) ⋅ A ) )" by (rule MMI_3coml)
   from S11 have S12: "( ( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( C ⋅ A ) \<cdiv> B ) = ( ( C \<cdiv> B ) ⋅ A )" by (rule MMI_imp)
   from S4 S8 S12 show "( ( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( A \<cdiv> B ) ⋅ C ) = ( ( C \<cdiv> B ) ⋅ A )" by (rule MMI_3eqtr3d)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_div12t: 
   shows "( ( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( A ⋅ ( B \<cdiv> C ) ) = ( B ⋅ ( A \<cdiv> C ) )"
proof -
   have S1: "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ ( B \<cdiv> C ) ∈ ℂ ) ⟶ 
 ( A ⋅ ( B \<cdiv> C ) ) = ( ( B \<cdiv> C ) ⋅ A )" by (rule MMI_axmulcom)
   have S2: "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ⟶ A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_3simp1)
   from S2 have S3: "( ( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   have S4: "( B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( B \<cdiv> C ) ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_divclt)
   from S4 have S5: "( ( B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( B \<cdiv> C ) ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_3expa)
   from S5 have S6: "( ( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( B \<cdiv> C ) ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_3adantl1)
   from S1 S3 S6 have S7: "( ( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( A ⋅ ( B \<cdiv> C ) ) = ( ( B \<cdiv> C ) ⋅ A )" by (rule MMI_sylanc)
   have S8: "( ( B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ∧ A ∈ ℂ ) ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( B \<cdiv> C ) ⋅ A ) = ( ( A \<cdiv> C ) ⋅ B )" by (rule MMI_div13t)
   from S8 have S9: "( B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ∧ A ∈ ℂ ) ⟶ 
 ( C ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
 ( ( B \<cdiv> C ) ⋅ A ) = 
 ( ( A \<cdiv> C ) ⋅ B ) )" by (rule MMI_ex)
   from S9 have S10: "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ⟶ 
 ( C ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
 ( ( B \<cdiv> C ) ⋅ A ) = 
 ( ( A \<cdiv> C ) ⋅ B ) )" by (rule MMI_3comr)
   from S10 have S11: "( ( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( B \<cdiv> C ) ⋅ A ) = ( ( A \<cdiv> C ) ⋅ B )" by (rule MMI_imp)
   have S12: "( ( A \<cdiv> C ) ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ) ⟶ 
 ( ( A \<cdiv> C ) ⋅ B ) = ( B ⋅ ( A \<cdiv> C ) )" by (rule MMI_axmulcom)
   have S13: "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( A \<cdiv> C ) ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_divclt)
   from S13 have S14: "( ( A ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( A \<cdiv> C ) ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_3expa)
   from S14 have S15: "( ( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( A \<cdiv> C ) ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_3adantl2)
   have S16: "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ⟶ B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_3simp2)
   from S16 have S17: "( ( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   from S12 S15 S17 have S18: "( ( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( A \<cdiv> C ) ⋅ B ) = ( B ⋅ ( A \<cdiv> C ) )" by (rule MMI_sylanc)
   from S7 S11 S18 show "( ( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( A ⋅ ( B \<cdiv> C ) ) = ( B ⋅ ( A \<cdiv> C ) )" by (rule MMI_3eqtrd)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_divassz: assumes A1: "A ∈ ℂ" and
    A2: "B ∈ ℂ" and
    A3: "C ∈ ℂ"   
   shows "C ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
 ( ( A ⋅ B ) \<cdiv> C ) = ( A ⋅ ( B \<cdiv> C ) )"
proof -
   from A1 have S1: "A ∈ ℂ".
   from A2 have S2: "B ∈ ℂ".
   from A3 have S3: "C ∈ ℂ".
   from S1 S2 S3 have S4: "A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_3pm3_2i)
   have S5: "( ( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( A ⋅ B ) \<cdiv> C ) = ( A ⋅ ( B \<cdiv> C ) )" by (rule MMI_divasst)
   from S4 S5 show "C ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
 ( ( A ⋅ B ) \<cdiv> C ) = ( A ⋅ ( B \<cdiv> C ) )" by (rule MMI_mpan)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_divass: assumes A1: "A ∈ ℂ" and
    A2: "B ∈ ℂ" and
    A3: "C ∈ ℂ" and
    A4: "C ≠ 𝟬"   
   shows "( ( A ⋅ B ) \<cdiv> C ) = ( A ⋅ ( B \<cdiv> C ) )"
proof -
   from A4 have S1: "C ≠ 𝟬".
   from A1 have S2: "A ∈ ℂ".
   from A2 have S3: "B ∈ ℂ".
   from A3 have S4: "C ∈ ℂ".
   from S2 S3 S4 have S5: "C ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
 ( ( A ⋅ B ) \<cdiv> C ) = ( A ⋅ ( B \<cdiv> C ) )" by (rule MMI_divassz)
   from S1 S5 show "( ( A ⋅ B ) \<cdiv> C ) = ( A ⋅ ( B \<cdiv> C ) )" by (rule MMI_ax_mp)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_divdir: assumes A1: "A ∈ ℂ" and
    A2: "B ∈ ℂ" and
    A3: "C ∈ ℂ" and
    A4: "C ≠ 𝟬"   
   shows "( ( A \<ca> B ) \<cdiv> C ) = 
 ( ( A \<cdiv> C ) \<ca> ( B \<cdiv> C ) )"
proof -
   from A1 have S1: "A ∈ ℂ".
   from A2 have S2: "B ∈ ℂ".
   from A3 have S3: "C ∈ ℂ".
   from A4 have S4: "C ≠ 𝟬".
   from S3 S4 have S5: "( 𝟭 \<cdiv> C ) ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_reccl)
   from S1 S2 S5 have S6: "( ( A \<ca> B ) ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> C ) ) = 
 ( ( A ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> C ) ) \<ca> ( B ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> C ) ) )" by (rule MMI_adddir)
   from A1 have S7: "A ∈ ℂ".
   from A2 have S8: "B ∈ ℂ".
   from S7 S8 have S9: "( A \<ca> B ) ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_addcl)
   from A3 have S10: "C ∈ ℂ".
   from A4 have S11: "C ≠ 𝟬".
   from S9 S10 S11 have S12: "( ( A \<ca> B ) \<cdiv> C ) = 
 ( ( A \<ca> B ) ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> C ) )" by (rule MMI_divrec)
   from A1 have S13: "A ∈ ℂ".
   from A3 have S14: "C ∈ ℂ".
   from A4 have S15: "C ≠ 𝟬".
   from S13 S14 S15 have S16: "( A \<cdiv> C ) = ( A ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> C ) )" by (rule MMI_divrec)
   from A2 have S17: "B ∈ ℂ".
   from A3 have S18: "C ∈ ℂ".
   from A4 have S19: "C ≠ 𝟬".
   from S17 S18 S19 have S20: "( B \<cdiv> C ) = ( B ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> C ) )" by (rule MMI_divrec)
   from S16 S20 have S21: "( ( A \<cdiv> C ) \<ca> ( B \<cdiv> C ) ) = 
 ( ( A ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> C ) ) \<ca> ( B ⋅ ( 𝟭 \<cdiv> C ) ) )" by (rule MMI_opreq12i)
   from S6 S12 S21 show "( ( A \<ca> B ) \<cdiv> C ) = 
 ( ( A \<cdiv> C ) \<ca> ( B \<cdiv> C ) )" by (rule MMI_3eqtr4)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_div23: assumes A1: "A ∈ ℂ" and
    A2: "B ∈ ℂ" and
    A3: "C ∈ ℂ" and
    A4: "C ≠ 𝟬"   
   shows "( ( A ⋅ B ) \<cdiv> C ) = ( ( A \<cdiv> C ) ⋅ B )"
proof -
   from A1 have S1: "A ∈ ℂ".
   from A2 have S2: "B ∈ ℂ".
   from S1 S2 have S3: "( A ⋅ B ) = ( B ⋅ A )" by (rule MMI_mulcom)
   from S3 have S4: "( ( A ⋅ B ) \<cdiv> C ) = ( ( B ⋅ A ) \<cdiv> C )" 
     by (rule MMI_opreq1i)
   from A2 have S5: "B ∈ ℂ".
   from A1 have S6: "A ∈ ℂ".
   from A3 have S7: "C ∈ ℂ".
   from A4 have S8: "C ≠ 𝟬".
   from S5 S6 S7 S8 have 
     S9: "( ( B ⋅ A ) \<cdiv> C ) = ( B ⋅ ( A \<cdiv> C ) )" by (rule MMI_divass)
   from A2 have S10: "B ∈ ℂ".
   from A1 have S11: "A ∈ ℂ".
   from A3 have S12: "C ∈ ℂ".
   from A4 have S13: "C ≠ 𝟬".
   from S11 S12 S13 have S14: "( A \<cdiv> C ) ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_divcl)
   from S10 S14 have S15: "( B ⋅ ( A \<cdiv> C ) ) = ( ( A \<cdiv> C ) ⋅ B )" 
     by (rule MMI_mulcom)
   from S4 S9 S15 show "( ( A ⋅ B ) \<cdiv> C ) = ( ( A \<cdiv> C ) ⋅ B )" 
     by (rule MMI_3eqtr)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_divdirz: assumes A1: "A ∈ ℂ" and
    A2: "B ∈ ℂ" and
    A3: "C ∈ ℂ"   
   shows "C ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
 ( ( A \<ca> B ) \<cdiv> C ) = 
 ( ( A \<cdiv> C ) \<ca> ( B \<cdiv> C ) )"
proof -
   have S1: "C = 
 if ( C ≠ 𝟬 , C , 𝟭 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( A \<ca> B ) \<cdiv> C ) = 
 ( ( A \<ca> B ) \<cdiv> if ( C ≠ 𝟬 , C , 𝟭 ) )" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   have S2: "C = 
 if ( C ≠ 𝟬 , C , 𝟭 ) ⟶ 
 ( A \<cdiv> C ) = 
 ( A \<cdiv> if ( C ≠ 𝟬 , C , 𝟭 ) )" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   have S3: "C = 
 if ( C ≠ 𝟬 , C , 𝟭 ) ⟶ 
 ( B \<cdiv> C ) = 
 ( B \<cdiv> if ( C ≠ 𝟬 , C , 𝟭 ) )" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   from S2 S3 have S4: "C = 
 if ( C ≠ 𝟬 , C , 𝟭 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( A \<cdiv> C ) \<ca> ( B \<cdiv> C ) ) = 
 ( ( A \<cdiv> if ( C ≠ 𝟬 , C , 𝟭 ) ) \<ca> ( B \<cdiv> if ( C ≠ 𝟬 , C , 𝟭 ) ) )" by (rule MMI_opreq12d)
   from S1 S4 have S5: "C = 
 if ( C ≠ 𝟬 , C , 𝟭 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( ( A \<ca> B ) \<cdiv> C ) = 
 ( ( A \<cdiv> C ) \<ca> ( B \<cdiv> C ) ) ⟷ 
 ( ( A \<ca> B ) \<cdiv> if ( C ≠ 𝟬 , C , 𝟭 ) ) = 
 ( ( A \<cdiv> if ( C ≠ 𝟬 , C , 𝟭 ) ) \<ca> ( B \<cdiv> if ( C ≠ 𝟬 , C , 𝟭 ) ) ) )" by (rule MMI_eqeq12d)
   from A1 have S6: "A ∈ ℂ".
   from A2 have S7: "B ∈ ℂ".
   from A3 have S8: "C ∈ ℂ".
   have S9: "𝟭 ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_1cn)
   from S8 S9 have S10: "if ( C ≠ 𝟬 , C , 𝟭 ) ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_keepel)
   have S11: "if ( C ≠ 𝟬 , C , 𝟭 ) ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_elimne0)
   from S6 S7 S10 S11 have S12: "( ( A \<ca> B ) \<cdiv> if ( C ≠ 𝟬 , C , 𝟭 ) ) = 
 ( ( A \<cdiv> if ( C ≠ 𝟬 , C , 𝟭 ) ) \<ca> ( B \<cdiv> if ( C ≠ 𝟬 , C , 𝟭 ) ) )" by (rule MMI_divdir)
   from S5 S12 show "C ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
 ( ( A \<ca> B ) \<cdiv> C ) = 
 ( ( A \<cdiv> C ) \<ca> ( B \<cdiv> C ) )" by (rule MMI_dedth)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_divdirt: 
   shows "( ( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( A \<ca> B ) \<cdiv> C ) = 
 ( ( A \<cdiv> C ) \<ca> ( B \<cdiv> C ) )"
proof -
   have S1: "A = 
 if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( A \<ca> B ) = 
 ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) \<ca> B )" by (rule MMI_opreq1)
   from S1 have S2: "A = 
 if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( A \<ca> B ) \<cdiv> C ) = 
 ( ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) \<ca> B ) \<cdiv> C )" by (rule MMI_opreq1d)
   have S3: "A = 
 if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( A \<cdiv> C ) = 
 ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) \<cdiv> C )" by (rule MMI_opreq1)
   from S3 have S4: "A = 
 if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( A \<cdiv> C ) \<ca> ( B \<cdiv> C ) ) = 
 ( ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) \<cdiv> C ) \<ca> ( B \<cdiv> C ) )" by (rule MMI_opreq1d)
   from S2 S4 have S5: "A = 
 if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( ( A \<ca> B ) \<cdiv> C ) = 
 ( ( A \<cdiv> C ) \<ca> ( B \<cdiv> C ) ) ⟷ 
 ( ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) \<ca> B ) \<cdiv> C ) = 
 ( ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) \<cdiv> C ) \<ca> ( B \<cdiv> C ) ) )" by (rule MMI_eqeq12d)
   from S5 have S6: "A = 
 if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( C ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ ( ( A \<ca> B ) \<cdiv> C ) = ( ( A \<cdiv> C ) \<ca> ( B \<cdiv> C ) ) ) ⟷ 
 ( C ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
 ( ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) \<ca> B ) \<cdiv> C ) = 
 ( ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) \<cdiv> C ) \<ca> ( B \<cdiv> C ) ) ) )" by (rule MMI_imbi2d)
   have S7: "B = 
 if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) \<ca> B ) = 
 ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) \<ca> if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) )" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   from S7 have S8: "B = 
 if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) \<ca> B ) \<cdiv> C ) = 
 ( ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) \<ca> if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) ) \<cdiv> C )" by (rule MMI_opreq1d)
   have S9: "B = 
 if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( B \<cdiv> C ) = 
 ( if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) \<cdiv> C )" by (rule MMI_opreq1)
   from S9 have S10: "B = 
 if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) \<cdiv> C ) \<ca> ( B \<cdiv> C ) ) = 
 ( ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) \<cdiv> C ) \<ca> ( if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) \<cdiv> C ) )" by (rule MMI_opreq2d)
   from S8 S10 have S11: "B = 
 if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) \<ca> B ) \<cdiv> C ) = 
 ( ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) \<cdiv> C ) \<ca> ( B \<cdiv> C ) ) ⟷ 
 ( ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) \<ca> if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) ) \<cdiv> C ) = 
 ( ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) \<cdiv> C ) \<ca> ( if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) \<cdiv> C ) ) )" by (rule MMI_eqeq12d)
   from S11 have S12: "B = 
 if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( C ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ ( ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) \<ca> B ) \<cdiv> C ) = ( ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) \<cdiv> C ) \<ca> ( B \<cdiv> C ) ) ) ⟷ 
 ( C ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
 ( ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) \<ca> if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) ) \<cdiv> C ) = 
 ( ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) \<cdiv> C ) \<ca> ( if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) \<cdiv> C ) ) ) )" by (rule MMI_imbi2d)
   have S13: "C = 
 if ( C ∈ ℂ , C , 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( C ≠ 𝟬 ⟷ if ( C ∈ ℂ , C , 𝟬 ) ≠ 𝟬 )" by (rule MMI_neeq1)
   have S14: "C = 
 if ( C ∈ ℂ , C , 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) \<ca> if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) ) \<cdiv> C ) = 
 ( ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) \<ca> if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) ) \<cdiv> if ( C ∈ ℂ , C , 𝟬 ) )" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   have S15: "C = 
 if ( C ∈ ℂ , C , 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) \<cdiv> C ) = 
 ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) \<cdiv> if ( C ∈ ℂ , C , 𝟬 ) )" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   have S16: "C = 
 if ( C ∈ ℂ , C , 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) \<cdiv> C ) = 
 ( if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) \<cdiv> if ( C ∈ ℂ , C , 𝟬 ) )" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   from S15 S16 have S17: "C = 
 if ( C ∈ ℂ , C , 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) \<cdiv> C ) \<ca> ( if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) \<cdiv> C ) ) = 
 ( ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) \<cdiv> if ( C ∈ ℂ , C , 𝟬 ) ) \<ca> ( if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) \<cdiv> if ( C ∈ ℂ , C , 𝟬 ) ) )" by (rule MMI_opreq12d)
   from S14 S17 have S18: "C = 
 if ( C ∈ ℂ , C , 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) \<ca> if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) ) \<cdiv> C ) = 
 ( ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) \<cdiv> C ) \<ca> ( if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) \<cdiv> C ) ) ⟷ 
 ( ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) \<ca> if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) ) \<cdiv> if ( C ∈ ℂ , C , 𝟬 ) ) = 
 ( ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) \<cdiv> if ( C ∈ ℂ , C , 𝟬 ) ) \<ca> ( if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) \<cdiv> if ( C ∈ ℂ , C , 𝟬 ) ) ) )" by (rule MMI_eqeq12d)
   from S13 S18 have S19: "C = 
 if ( C ∈ ℂ , C , 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( C ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ ( ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) \<ca> if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) ) \<cdiv> C ) = ( ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) \<cdiv> C ) \<ca> ( if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) \<cdiv> C ) ) ) ⟷ 
 ( if ( C ∈ ℂ , C , 𝟬 ) ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
 ( ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) \<ca> if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) ) \<cdiv> if ( C ∈ ℂ , C , 𝟬 ) ) = 
 ( ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) \<cdiv> if ( C ∈ ℂ , C , 𝟬 ) ) \<ca> ( if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) \<cdiv> if ( C ∈ ℂ , C , 𝟬 ) ) ) ) )" by (rule MMI_imbi12d)
   have S20: "𝟬 ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_0cn)
   from S20 have S21: "if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   have S22: "𝟬 ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_0cn)
   from S22 have S23: "if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   have S24: "𝟬 ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_0cn)
   from S24 have S25: "if ( C ∈ ℂ , C , 𝟬 ) ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   from S21 S23 S25 have S26: "if ( C ∈ ℂ , C , 𝟬 ) ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
 ( ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) \<ca> if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) ) \<cdiv> if ( C ∈ ℂ , C , 𝟬 ) ) = 
 ( ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) \<cdiv> if ( C ∈ ℂ , C , 𝟬 ) ) \<ca> ( if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) \<cdiv> if ( C ∈ ℂ , C , 𝟬 ) ) )" by (rule MMI_divdirz)
   from S6 S12 S19 S26 have S27: "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ⟶ 
 ( C ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
 ( ( A \<ca> B ) \<cdiv> C ) = 
 ( ( A \<cdiv> C ) \<ca> ( B \<cdiv> C ) ) )" by (rule MMI_dedth3h)
   from S27 show "( ( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ) ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( A \<ca> B ) \<cdiv> C ) = 
 ( ( A \<cdiv> C ) \<ca> ( B \<cdiv> C ) )" by (rule MMI_imp)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_divcan3: assumes A1: "A ∈ ℂ" and
    A2: "B ∈ ℂ" and
    A3: "A ≠ 𝟬"   
   shows "( ( A ⋅ B ) \<cdiv> A ) = B"
proof -
   from A1 have S1: "A ∈ ℂ".
   from A2 have S2: "B ∈ ℂ".
   from A1 have S3: "A ∈ ℂ".
   from A3 have S4: "A ≠ 𝟬".
   from S1 S2 S3 S4 have S5: "( ( A ⋅ B ) \<cdiv> A ) = ( A ⋅ ( B \<cdiv> A ) )" by (rule MMI_divass)
   from A1 have S6: "A ∈ ℂ".
   from A2 have S7: "B ∈ ℂ".
   from A3 have S8: "A ≠ 𝟬".
   from S6 S7 S8 have S9: "( A ⋅ ( B \<cdiv> A ) ) = B" by (rule MMI_divcan2)
   from S5 S9 show "( ( A ⋅ B ) \<cdiv> A ) = B" by (rule MMI_eqtr)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_divcan4: assumes A1: "A ∈ ℂ" and
    A2: "B ∈ ℂ" and
    A3: "A ≠ 𝟬"   
   shows "( ( B ⋅ A ) \<cdiv> A ) = B"
proof -
   from A2 have S1: "B ∈ ℂ".
   from A1 have S2: "A ∈ ℂ".
   from S1 S2 have S3: "( B ⋅ A ) = ( A ⋅ B )" by (rule MMI_mulcom)
   from S3 have S4: "( ( B ⋅ A ) \<cdiv> A ) = ( ( A ⋅ B ) \<cdiv> A )" by (rule MMI_opreq1i)
   from A1 have S5: "A ∈ ℂ".
   from A2 have S6: "B ∈ ℂ".
   from A3 have S7: "A ≠ 𝟬".
   from S5 S6 S7 have S8: "( ( A ⋅ B ) \<cdiv> A ) = B" by (rule MMI_divcan3)
   from S4 S8 show "( ( B ⋅ A ) \<cdiv> A ) = B" by (rule MMI_eqtr)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_divcan3z: assumes A1: "A ∈ ℂ" and
    A2: "B ∈ ℂ"   
   shows "A ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ ( ( A ⋅ B ) \<cdiv> A ) = B"
proof -
   have S1: "A = 
 if ( A ≠ 𝟬 , A , 𝟭 ) ⟶ 
 ( A ⋅ B ) = 
 ( if ( A ≠ 𝟬 , A , 𝟭 ) ⋅ B )" by (rule MMI_opreq1)
   have S2: "A = 
 if ( A ≠ 𝟬 , A , 𝟭 ) ⟶ 
 A = if ( A ≠ 𝟬 , A , 𝟭 )" by (rule MMI_id)
   from S1 S2 have S3: "A = 
 if ( A ≠ 𝟬 , A , 𝟭 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( A ⋅ B ) \<cdiv> A ) = 
 ( ( if ( A ≠ 𝟬 , A , 𝟭 ) ⋅ B ) \<cdiv> if ( A ≠ 𝟬 , A , 𝟭 ) )" by (rule MMI_opreq12d)
   from S3 have S4: "A = 
 if ( A ≠ 𝟬 , A , 𝟭 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( ( A ⋅ B ) \<cdiv> A ) = 
 B ⟷ 
 ( ( if ( A ≠ 𝟬 , A , 𝟭 ) ⋅ B ) \<cdiv> if ( A ≠ 𝟬 , A , 𝟭 ) ) = 
 B )" by (rule MMI_eqeq1d)
   from A1 have S5: "A ∈ ℂ".
   have S6: "𝟭 ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_1cn)
   from S5 S6 have S7: "if ( A ≠ 𝟬 , A , 𝟭 ) ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_keepel)
   from A2 have S8: "B ∈ ℂ".
   have S9: "if ( A ≠ 𝟬 , A , 𝟭 ) ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_elimne0)
   from S7 S8 S9 have S10: "( ( if ( A ≠ 𝟬 , A , 𝟭 ) ⋅ B ) \<cdiv> if ( A ≠ 𝟬 , A , 𝟭 ) ) = 
 B" by (rule MMI_divcan3)
   from S4 S10 show "A ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ ( ( A ⋅ B ) \<cdiv> A ) = B" by (rule MMI_dedth)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_divcan4z: assumes A1: "A ∈ ℂ" and
    A2: "B ∈ ℂ"   
   shows "A ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ ( ( B ⋅ A ) \<cdiv> A ) = B"
proof -
   from A1 have S1: "A ∈ ℂ".
   from A2 have S2: "B ∈ ℂ".
   from S1 S2 have S3: "A ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ ( ( A ⋅ B ) \<cdiv> A ) = B" by (rule MMI_divcan3z)
   from A2 have S4: "B ∈ ℂ".
   from A1 have S5: "A ∈ ℂ".
   from S4 S5 have S6: "( B ⋅ A ) = ( A ⋅ B )" by (rule MMI_mulcom)
   from S6 have S7: "( ( B ⋅ A ) \<cdiv> A ) = ( ( A ⋅ B ) \<cdiv> A )" by (rule MMI_opreq1i)
   from S3 S7 show "A ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ ( ( B ⋅ A ) \<cdiv> A ) = B" by (rule MMI_syl5eq)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_divcan3t: 
   shows "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ A ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( A ⋅ B ) \<cdiv> A ) = B"
proof -
   have S1: "A = 
 if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( A ≠ 𝟬 ⟷ if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ≠ 𝟬 )" by (rule MMI_neeq1)
   have S2: "A = 
 if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( A ⋅ B ) = 
 ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⋅ B )" by (rule MMI_opreq1)
   have S3: "A = 
 if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 A = if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 )" by (rule MMI_id)
   from S2 S3 have S4: "A = 
 if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( A ⋅ B ) \<cdiv> A ) = 
 ( ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⋅ B ) \<cdiv> if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) )" by (rule MMI_opreq12d)
   from S4 have S5: "A = 
 if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( ( A ⋅ B ) \<cdiv> A ) = 
 B ⟷ 
 ( ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⋅ B ) \<cdiv> if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ) = 
 B )" by (rule MMI_eqeq1d)
   from S1 S5 have S6: "A = 
 if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( A ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ ( ( A ⋅ B ) \<cdiv> A ) = B ) ⟷ 
 ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
 ( ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⋅ B ) \<cdiv> if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ) = 
 B ) )" by (rule MMI_imbi12d)
   have S7: "B = 
 if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⋅ B ) = 
 ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⋅ if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) )" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   from S7 have S8: "B = 
 if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⋅ B ) \<cdiv> if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ) = 
 ( ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⋅ if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) ) \<cdiv> if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) )" by (rule MMI_opreq1d)
   have S9: "B = 
 if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 B = if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 )" by (rule MMI_id)
   from S8 S9 have S10: "B = 
 if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⋅ B ) \<cdiv> if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ) = 
 B ⟷ 
 ( ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⋅ if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) ) \<cdiv> if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ) = 
 if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) )" by (rule MMI_eqeq12d)
   from S10 have S11: "B = 
 if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ ( ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⋅ B ) \<cdiv> if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ) = B ) ⟷ 
 ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
 ( ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⋅ if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) ) \<cdiv> if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ) = 
 if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) ) )" by (rule MMI_imbi2d)
   have S12: "𝟬 ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_0cn)
   from S12 have S13: "if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   have S14: "𝟬 ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_0cn)
   from S14 have S15: "if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   from S13 S15 have S16: "if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
 ( ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ⋅ if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 ) ) \<cdiv> if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟬 ) ) = 
 if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟬 )" by (rule MMI_divcan3z)
   from S6 S11 S16 have S17: "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ) ⟶ 
 ( A ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ ( ( A ⋅ B ) \<cdiv> A ) = B )" by (rule MMI_dedth2h)
   from S17 show "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ A ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( A ⋅ B ) \<cdiv> A ) = B" by (rule MMI_3impia)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_divcan4t: 
   shows "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ A ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( B ⋅ A ) \<cdiv> A ) = B"
proof -
   have S1: "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ) ⟶ 
 ( A ⋅ B ) = ( B ⋅ A )" by (rule MMI_axmulcom)
   from S1 have S2: "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ) ⟶ 
 ( ( A ⋅ B ) \<cdiv> A ) = ( ( B ⋅ A ) \<cdiv> A )" by (rule MMI_opreq1d)
   from S2 have S3: "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ A ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( A ⋅ B ) \<cdiv> A ) = ( ( B ⋅ A ) \<cdiv> A )" by (rule MMI_3adant3)
   have S4: "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ A ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( A ⋅ B ) \<cdiv> A ) = B" by (rule MMI_divcan3t)
   from S3 S4 show "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ A ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( B ⋅ A ) \<cdiv> A ) = B" by (rule MMI_eqtr3d)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_div11: assumes A1: "A ∈ ℂ" and
    A2: "B ∈ ℂ" and
    A3: "C ∈ ℂ" and
    A4: "C ≠ 𝟬"   
   shows "( A \<cdiv> C ) = ( B \<cdiv> C ) ⟷ A = B"
proof -
   from A3 have S1: "C ∈ ℂ".
   from A1 have S2: "A ∈ ℂ".
   from A3 have S3: "C ∈ ℂ".
   from A4 have S4: "C ≠ 𝟬".
   from S2 S3 S4 have S5: "( A \<cdiv> C ) ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_divcl)
   from A2 have S6: "B ∈ ℂ".
   from A3 have S7: "C ∈ ℂ".
   from A4 have S8: "C ≠ 𝟬".
   from S6 S7 S8 have S9: "( B \<cdiv> C ) ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_divcl)
   from A4 have S10: "C ≠ 𝟬".
   from S1 S5 S9 S10 have S11: "( C ⋅ ( A \<cdiv> C ) ) = 
 ( C ⋅ ( B \<cdiv> C ) ) ⟷ 
 ( A \<cdiv> C ) = ( B \<cdiv> C )" by (rule MMI_mulcan)
   from A3 have S12: "C ∈ ℂ".
   from A1 have S13: "A ∈ ℂ".
   from A4 have S14: "C ≠ 𝟬".
   from S12 S13 S14 have S15: "( C ⋅ ( A \<cdiv> C ) ) = A" by (rule MMI_divcan2)
   from A3 have S16: "C ∈ ℂ".
   from A2 have S17: "B ∈ ℂ".
   from A4 have S18: "C ≠ 𝟬".
   from S16 S17 S18 have S19: "( C ⋅ ( B \<cdiv> C ) ) = B" by (rule MMI_divcan2)
   from S15 S19 have S20: "( C ⋅ ( A \<cdiv> C ) ) = 
 ( C ⋅ ( B \<cdiv> C ) ) ⟷ A = B" by (rule MMI_eqeq12i)
   from S11 S20 show "( A \<cdiv> C ) = ( B \<cdiv> C ) ⟷ A = B" by (rule MMI_bitr3)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_div11t: 
   shows "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ ( C ∈ ℂ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) ) ⟶ 
 ( ( A \<cdiv> C ) = ( B \<cdiv> C ) ⟷ A = B )"
proof -
   have S1: "A = 
 if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟭 ) ⟶ 
 ( A \<cdiv> C ) = 
 ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟭 ) \<cdiv> C )" by (rule MMI_opreq1)
   from S1 have S2: "A = 
 if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟭 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( A \<cdiv> C ) = 
 ( B \<cdiv> C ) ⟷ 
 ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟭 ) \<cdiv> C ) = 
 ( B \<cdiv> C ) )" by (rule MMI_eqeq1d)
   have S3: "A = 
 if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟭 ) ⟶ 
 ( A = B ⟷ if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟭 ) = B )" by (rule MMI_eqeq1)
   from S2 S3 have S4: "A = 
 if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟭 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( ( A \<cdiv> C ) = ( B \<cdiv> C ) ⟷ A = B ) ⟷ 
 ( ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟭 ) \<cdiv> C ) = 
 ( B \<cdiv> C ) ⟷ 
 if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟭 ) = B ) )" by (rule MMI_bibi12d)
   have S5: "B = 
 if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟭 ) ⟶ 
 ( B \<cdiv> C ) = 
 ( if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟭 ) \<cdiv> C )" by (rule MMI_opreq1)
   from S5 have S6: "B = 
 if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟭 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟭 ) \<cdiv> C ) = 
 ( B \<cdiv> C ) ⟷ 
 ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟭 ) \<cdiv> C ) = 
 ( if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟭 ) \<cdiv> C ) )" by (rule MMI_eqeq2d)
   have S7: "B = 
 if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟭 ) ⟶ 
 ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟭 ) = 
 B ⟷ 
 if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟭 ) = 
 if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟭 ) )" by (rule MMI_eqeq2)
   from S6 S7 have S8: "B = 
 if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟭 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟭 ) \<cdiv> C ) = ( B \<cdiv> C ) ⟷ if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟭 ) = B ) ⟷ 
 ( ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟭 ) \<cdiv> C ) = 
 ( if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟭 ) \<cdiv> C ) ⟷ 
 if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟭 ) = 
 if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟭 ) ) )" by (rule MMI_bibi12d)
   have S9: "C = 
 if ( ( C ∈ ℂ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) , C , 𝟭 ) ⟶ 
 ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟭 ) \<cdiv> C ) = 
 ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟭 ) \<cdiv> if ( ( C ∈ ℂ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) , C , 𝟭 ) )" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   have S10: "C = 
 if ( ( C ∈ ℂ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) , C , 𝟭 ) ⟶ 
 ( if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟭 ) \<cdiv> C ) = 
 ( if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟭 ) \<cdiv> if ( ( C ∈ ℂ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) , C , 𝟭 ) )" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   from S9 S10 have S11: "C = 
 if ( ( C ∈ ℂ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) , C , 𝟭 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟭 ) \<cdiv> C ) = 
 ( if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟭 ) \<cdiv> C ) ⟷ 
 ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟭 ) \<cdiv> if ( ( C ∈ ℂ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) , C , 𝟭 ) ) = 
 ( if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟭 ) \<cdiv> if ( ( C ∈ ℂ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) , C , 𝟭 ) ) )" by (rule MMI_eqeq12d)
   from S11 have S12: "C = 
 if ( ( C ∈ ℂ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) , C , 𝟭 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟭 ) \<cdiv> C ) = ( if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟭 ) \<cdiv> C ) ⟷ if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟭 ) = if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟭 ) ) ⟷ 
 ( ( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟭 ) \<cdiv> if ( ( C ∈ ℂ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) , C , 𝟭 ) ) = 
 ( if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟭 ) \<cdiv> if ( ( C ∈ ℂ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) , C , 𝟭 ) ) ⟷ 
 if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟭 ) = 
 if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟭 ) ) )" by (rule MMI_bibi1d)
   have S13: "𝟭 ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_1cn)
   from S13 have S14: "if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟭 ) ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   have S15: "𝟭 ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_1cn)
   from S15 have S16: "if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟭 ) ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   have S17: "C = 
 if ( ( C ∈ ℂ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) , C , 𝟭 ) ⟶ 
 ( C ∈ ℂ ⟷ 
 if ( ( C ∈ ℂ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) , C , 𝟭 ) ∈ ℂ )" by (rule MMI_eleq1)
   have S18: "C = 
 if ( ( C ∈ ℂ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) , C , 𝟭 ) ⟶ 
 ( C ≠ 𝟬 ⟷ 
 if ( ( C ∈ ℂ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) , C , 𝟭 ) ≠ 𝟬 )" by (rule MMI_neeq1)
   from S17 S18 have S19: "C = 
 if ( ( C ∈ ℂ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) , C , 𝟭 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( C ∈ ℂ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟷ 
 ( if ( ( C ∈ ℂ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) , C , 𝟭 ) ∈ ℂ ∧ if ( ( C ∈ ℂ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) , C , 𝟭 ) ≠ 𝟬 ) )" by (rule MMI_anbi12d)
   have S20: "𝟭 = 
 if ( ( C ∈ ℂ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) , C , 𝟭 ) ⟶ 
 ( 𝟭 ∈ ℂ ⟷ 
 if ( ( C ∈ ℂ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) , C , 𝟭 ) ∈ ℂ )" by (rule MMI_eleq1)
   have S21: "𝟭 = 
 if ( ( C ∈ ℂ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) , C , 𝟭 ) ⟶ 
 ( 𝟭 ≠ 𝟬 ⟷ 
 if ( ( C ∈ ℂ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) , C , 𝟭 ) ≠ 𝟬 )" by (rule MMI_neeq1)
   from S20 S21 have S22: "𝟭 = 
 if ( ( C ∈ ℂ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) , C , 𝟭 ) ⟶ 
 ( ( 𝟭 ∈ ℂ ∧ 𝟭 ≠ 𝟬 ) ⟷ 
 ( if ( ( C ∈ ℂ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) , C , 𝟭 ) ∈ ℂ ∧ if ( ( C ∈ ℂ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) , C , 𝟭 ) ≠ 𝟬 ) )" by (rule MMI_anbi12d)
   have S23: "𝟭 ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_1cn)
   have S24: "𝟭 ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_ax1ne0)
   from S23 S24 have S25: "𝟭 ∈ ℂ ∧ 𝟭 ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_pm3_2i)
   from S19 S22 S25 have S26: "if ( ( C ∈ ℂ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) , C , 𝟭 ) ∈ ℂ ∧ if ( ( C ∈ ℂ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) , C , 𝟭 ) ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_elimhyp)
   from S26 have S27: "if ( ( C ∈ ℂ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) , C , 𝟭 ) ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_pm3_26i)
   from S26 have S28: "if ( ( C ∈ ℂ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) , C , 𝟭 ) ∈ ℂ ∧ if ( ( C ∈ ℂ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) , C , 𝟭 ) ≠ 𝟬" .
   from S28 have S29: "if ( ( C ∈ ℂ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) , C , 𝟭 ) ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_pm3_27i)
   from S14 S16 S27 S29 have S30: "( if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟭 ) \<cdiv> if ( ( C ∈ ℂ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) , C , 𝟭 ) ) = 
 ( if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟭 ) \<cdiv> if ( ( C ∈ ℂ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) , C , 𝟭 ) ) ⟷ 
 if ( A ∈ ℂ , A , 𝟭 ) = 
 if ( B ∈ ℂ , B , 𝟭 )" by (rule MMI_div11)
   from S4 S8 S12 S30 show "( A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ ( C ∈ ℂ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ) ) ⟶ 
 ( ( A \<cdiv> C ) = ( B \<cdiv> C ) ⟷ A = B )" by (rule MMI_dedth3h)
qed


end
